To '''boil''' [[water]] is to make it hot so that it begins to make [[Liquid bubble|bubbles]] and turns into [[steam]]. 

To boil [[food]] is to [[cook]] it in boiling water.

A boil of the skin is an infection is caused by the [[bacteria]] ''[[Staphylococcus aureus]]''.

